The Little Prince
https://imageserver.kitapyurdu.com/select.php?imageid=4448003&width=500&isWatermarked=true
2017-09-18
 9,25
This is the story of a child who lives in a little planet with his flower and wonders the other planets. One day, he decides to travel to the other planets to discover them and meet other people. Through the balloons, he starts to visit them but because of an accident he has to land on a desert.In fact, this book tells that how the people looks like through the eyes of an child. It is not only for children, but also for the adults. While reading it, you will understand the life, the people and also yourselves.
